[I] A library that allows manipulation of the iTunesDB

[T] ipod-sharp is a library that allows manipulation of the iTunesDB used in
[T] Apple iPod devices. Currently it supports adding/removing songs and
[T] manipulating playlists. Recent versions added the ability to manipulate
[T] the photo database and attach cover art.

[U] http://banshee-project.org/Ipod-sharp

